on (make a push for her second Olympics) four months ago, I would not even be here.\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that decision\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"a push\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"her second Olympics\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am trying to see it in that perspective - even though it wasn't my best performance or I did not come in the top five, I have to learn to be more grateful, and be kind to myself and my achievements.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that perspective\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1664}, {\"ngram\": \"my best performance\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1708}, {\"ngram\": \"my achievements\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just trying to sit with that feeling of being excited, I can not believe it's been four months since I went on this journey.\\\"\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1956, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that feeling\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"four months\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1925}, {\"ngram\": \"this journey\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aisyah, who won a SEA Games gold medal in 2013, is among several national athletes who have made the cut for the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 2086, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aisyah\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1964}, {\"ngram\": \"a SEA Games gold medal\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"several national athletes\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"the cut\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On April 20, kayaker Stephenie Chen had earned Singapore a spot at the quadrennial event.\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2119, \"end\": 2123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.or