 \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2313}, {\"ngram\": \"fencing\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After becoming thefirst Singaporean rower to feature at the Olympics in 2016, Aisyah took an indefinite break from competition in late 2017.\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2499}, {\"ngram\": \"Aisyah\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2515}, {\"ngram\": \"an indefinite break\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she began toying with the idea of making a qualifying bid for the Paris Games in early 2023, before deciding to take the plunge at the end of the year.\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2728, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"a qualifying bid\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2634}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2654}, {\"ngram\": \"the plunge\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2704}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2715}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last December, she recorded a tearful video of herself declaring her ambitions to make the 2024 Olympics, marking the start of an intense four months.\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tearful video\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2773}, {\"ngram\": \"her ambitions\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2808}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2834}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2853}, {\"ngram\": \"an intense four months\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"I had been giving myself a lot of excuses so I decided that I would make a declaration to myself.\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2990, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2923}, {\"ngram\": \"excuses\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 2934}, {\"ngram\": \"a declaration\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The decision that I made was really hard but looking back, it's crazy how things have fallen into place.\\\"\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3098, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The decision\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3005}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3073}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3096}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To prepare for the qualifiers, she moved from Boston, where she was living with her husband Ross Zuckerman, to Sydney for training.\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3231, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3146, \"end\": 3152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"score\": 0.9999267396017156, \"rank\": 6.33221735720256e-05, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\"}, {\"begin\": 3192, \"end\": 3196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ross_Geller\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0549334137805066e-16, \"text\": \"Ross\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ross_Geller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ross_Geller\"}, {\"begin\": 3211, \"end\": 3217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999999976989784, \"rank\": 1.4139101915466689e-09, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the qualifiers\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3129}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3230}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She felt lonely at times, but was grateful for the support from him and those around her.\", \"from\": 3233, \"to\": 3322, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3257}, {\"ngram\": \"the support\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While there were tough moments, she is also enjoying the experience of going through a second Olympic qualification campaign, expressing gratitude that her \\\"body still can take the pain\\\".\", \"from\": 3324, \"to\": 3511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tough moments\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3354}, {\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3391}, {\"ngram\": \"a second Olympic qualification campaign\", \"from\": 3409, \"to\": 3448}, {\"ngram\": \"gratitude\", \"from\": 3461, \"to\": 3470}, {\"ngram\": \"her \\\"body\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3485}, {\"ngram\": \"the pain\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bennett, who had coached Aisyah from 2013 till the 2016 Olympics, hailed her feat.\", \"from\": 3513, \"to\": 3595, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bennett\", \"from\": 3513, \"to\": 3520}, {\"ngram\": \"Aisyah\", \"from\": 3538, \"to\": 3544}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 Olympics\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3577}, {\"ngram\": \"her feat\", \"from\": 3586, \"to\": 3594}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"The fact that she has achieved her goal proves that if you have the desire and the ability, everything and anything is possible.\\\"\", \"from\": 3597, \"to\": 3736, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fact\", \"from\": 3607, \"to\": 3615}, {\"ngram\": \"her goal\", \"from\": 3638, \"to\": 3646}, {\"ngram\": \"the desire\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3681}, {\"ngram\": \"the ability\", \"from\": 3686, \"to\": 3697}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3709}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 3722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was also proud to see how much she had progressed over the past four months as she trained with the Sydney University Boat Club (SUBC).\", \"from\": 3738, \"to\": 3876, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3841, \"end\": 3868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney_University_Boat_Club\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sydney University Boat Club\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney_University_Boat_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney_University_Boat_Club\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past four months\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3816}, {\"ngram\": \"SUBC\", \"from\": 3870, \"to\": 3874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While she had already been sculling as part of her job as a trainer with rowing machine company Hydrow, he noted that being in a high-performance environment daily was very different.\", \"from\": 3878, \"to\": 4061, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 3921}, {\"ngram\": \"her job\", \"from\": 3925, \"to\": 3932}, {\"ngram\": \"a trainer\", \"from\": 3936, \"to\": 3945}, {\"ngram\": \"rowing machine company Hydrow\", \"from\": 3951, \"to\": 3980}, {\"ngram\": \"a high-performance environment\", \"from\": 4005, \"to\": 4035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bennett said: \\\"Being in the type of daily training environment she had at SUBC, where every athlete is pushing each other to be better every day and where there is programming, input and support from all of the coaches, allowed Aisyah to develop physically and technically into an even better rower than she was in 2016.\\\"\", \"from\": 4063, \"to\": 4385, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bennett\", \"from\": 4063, \"to\": 4070}, {\"ngram\": \"the type\", \"from\": 4087, \"to\": 4095}, {\"ngram\": \"daily training environment\", \"from\": 4099, \"to\": 4125}, {\"ngram\": \"SUBC\", \"from\": 4137, \"to\": 4141}, {\"ngram\": \"every athlete\", \"from\": 4149, \"to\": 4162}, {\"ngram\": \"programming\", \"from\": 4227, \"to\": 4238}, {\"ngram\": \"input\", \"from\": 4240, \"to\": 4245}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 4250, \"to\": 4257}, {\"ngram\": \"the coaches\", \"from\": 4270, \"to\": 4281}, {\"ngram\": \"Aisyah\", \"from\": 4291, \"to\": 4297}, {\"ngram\": \"an even better rower\", \"from\": 4341, \"to\": 4361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before she resumes her Games preparation in Boston, Aisyah is looking forward to being reunited with Zuckerman and enjoying a good steak, a birthday tradition that she missed out on when she turned 36 on April 20.\", \"from\": 4387, \"to\": 4600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4431, \"end\": 4437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"score\": 0.9999267396017156, \"rank\": 6.33221735720256e-05, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her Games preparation\", \"from\": 4406, \"to\": 4427}, {\"ngram\": \"Aisyah\", \"from\": 4439, \"to\": 4445}, {\"ngram\": \"Zuckerman\", \"from\": 4488, \"to\": 4497}, {\"ngram\": \"a good steak\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4523}, {\"ngram\": \"a birthday tradition\", \"from\": 4525, \"to\": 4545}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 4591, \"to\": 4596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"I want to go into Paris enjoying the journey and the moment because in Rio, I was just very overwhelmed and stressed that I did not really enjoy my whole experience.\", \"from\": 4602, \"to\": 4779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4632, \"end\": 4637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999236024, \"rank\": 7.643975997570156e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4685, \"end\": 4688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.82107608434264e-15, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the journey\", \"from\": 4647, \"to\": 4658}, {\"ngram\":